page.title: 13LIVING IN ETON WICK
page.content:
My name is{Matthew Tapp.}I am 11 years old. I live in a 3 bedroom semi - detached house. Most of my time is taken up with school and Scouts. I am an assistant Patrol Leader and Quarter Master Scout.I also hold my Master at Arms badge. I have been involved in Scouting for four years. I find it very interesting as I like outdoor life.
On school days I usually get up at quarter past seven. For breakfast I have toast and coffee. I will start getting dressed at half past seven and at 8 a.m. I will sit down and watch T.V. until 8.15. Then I will go round for James.
I like Eton Wick because it has a close community and everything is so near.
